Edited January 11, 2015 by lordyod
One of your mods has taken control of SAS. Try removing the stock bug fix modules, MechJeb, or FAR and see if that does anything.
It's unfortunately none of those. I'm currently deactivating mods one at a time trying to figure out what fixes it.
This is caused by Actions Everywhere. I experimented on removing/reinstalling it and turns out Actions Everywhere is the one that is spamming the SAS logs.
Thanks for the help! This solved it.
